{"id":383915,"date":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":22}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"235","ytitle":"","mtitle":"“海陆空军齐出动”","ftitle":"","authors":["赵幼庭"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘉兴农民　赵幼庭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的哥哥当海军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾着船儿去捞水草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一铲铲到水晶宫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急得“龙王”拼命逃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装回水草船船满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆起水草似山高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的嫂嫂当陆军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背着锄头去削野草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动锄头沙沙响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊得“土地”忙求饶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一堆堆草皮象摆阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒在河里做“人造尿”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下了我当空军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀上树枝采树梢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年古树低了头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慌得“玉帝”免了朝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采下树叶满河岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥拌树叶壅晚稻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风破浪过“四关”(注)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突击三昼夜搞肥料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海陆空军齐出动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的是晚稻超早稻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注)“四关”指抗旱、积肥、除虫、田间管理。"}]}